{"tid":813441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]台灣珍珠奶茶始祖春水堂登陸香港　9月西九龍高鐵站開業","createTime":"2018-09-10T12:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T05:22:54.000Z","uid":51546,"like":7,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"5106e610aa73a6c53cd0965055257824a82fa408","tid":813441,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"台灣老字號茶飲店春水堂是發明珍珠奶茶的始祖，無論是台灣本地人或是遊客，都極力推介春水堂出品的珍珠奶茶。繼登陸日本後，春水堂終於進駐香港！春水堂確認會在西九龍高鐵站開設香港首間分店，預計9月就會開業，珍珠奶茶迷又多個朝聖地方！<br />\n春水堂將台灣的當地小食粉圓加入茶飲當中，名為「珍珠奶茶」，之後旋即風靡整個台灣以至全球，掀起珍珠奶茶的熱潮。"},{"pid":"195738972ce7f948d8108aed074e2ec0d1c8d7d8","tid":813441,"uid":51546,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/w600/201809/20180910123528_8_chunshui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2Fw600%2F201809%2F20180910123528_8_chunshui.jpg&h=1621921f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eeec141798091c485887ead27edf24ac5973665","tid":813441,"uid":51546,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/1024x576/201809/20180910123528_9_chun.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2F1024x576%2F201809%2F20180910123528_9_chun.JPG&h=437d2393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0664a01bc51db8290bc6f6099f7d31c0cd483c6c","tid":813441,"uid":28800,"like":22,"dislike":95,"score":-73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a919db334b6c9165caabf0569eabf6cb0868e75a","tid":813441,"uid":51546,"like":96,"dislike":20,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"0664a01bc51db8290bc6f6099f7d31c0cd483c6c","tid":813441,"uid":28800,"like":22,"dislike":95,"score":-73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"大鄉里<img src=\