2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"我發現開咩都好  香港都有堆人話好好飲啊好正啊<br />\n其實真係咁多食家？ 我自問飲唔出分別<br />\n不如咁講啦  係咪因為香港d飲品太難飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25f428493617ab28cbd51bef41a37d3f171e394","tid":813441,"uid":11462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"珍珠奶茶 + 高鐵 <br />\n兩樣垃圾擺埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 一定好多有港女排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a14a34b00c5f84bf8593d166ab55766f9c14473","tid":813441,"uid":54929,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"認真，係台中飲過，仲要係第一鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲完都唔知同係街邊個啲有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係港女先鐘意飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e95f56a697b439d5650c232172dcb392ce43e34","tid":813441,"uid":89249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"今日先係板橋飲完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心一般，反而堂食唔錯"},{"pid":"027027164c66a38cae92a5c474b622b11a11507d","tid":813441,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"恰似一江春水向東流..."},{"pid":"ee39419469e7aa18efcf17cf5e1bd66bd9e05022","tid":813441,"uid":49197,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0664a01bc51db8290bc6f6099f7d31c0cd483c6c","tid":813441,"uid":28800,"like":22,"dislike":95,"score":-73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.youtube.com/